{"tid":1179535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國稀土生產商：料明年不再依賴中國提煉稀土","createTime":"2019-05-31T07:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:40:26.000Z","uid":227801,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba9784dd21cb4b56e5de6ab2bf038e5c75f517e","tid":1179535,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.944276/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.944276%2F2&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoOCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=ec2060df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.944276/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全美唯一稀土生產商Mountain Pass Materials聯席主席James Litinsky接受《CNBC》訪問時表示，預期公司明年可不再依賴中國，自行分離稀土物質，目前正尋求美國政府協助。他指全球除中國以外，並無提煉稀土的產能。他又表示，若他們不能經營，美國工業便沒有希望。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全美唯一稀土生產商Mountain Pass Materials聯席主席James Litinsky接受《CNBC》訪問時表示，預期公司明年可不再依賴中國，自行分離稀土物質，目前正尋求美國政府協助。他指全球除中國以外，並無提煉稀土的產能。他又表示，若他們不能經營，美國工業便沒有希望。<br />\n<br />\nMountain Pass每年向中國出口5萬噸稀土以進行提煉，早前中國就美國關稅作報復，向進口稀土開徵25%關稅，Mountain Pass成為受害者。(fc/u)"},{"pid":"19f0dd64731b06e32157126bdd9d19a9359f11ce","tid":1179535,"uid":64191,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"今日食飯茶記播TVB仲不停Loop稀土，場上親中人士拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40c2ca4b39842d0335457840c16dcdfdb375354","tid":1179535,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fc96873c6a2d3e9fd5ac3b03fcfa89a708565c1","tid":1179535,"uid":163350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0bf3db40a390ea04d30c6e1a2b701da24f4f19b","tid":1179535,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"呢次比美國重整工業"},{"pid":"29cff693a259746132947c4eca7d9